parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel System Contamination and Component Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel system contamination can cause fuel leaks, engine performance issues, and potentially lead to engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: engine runs rough with no power
black smoke coming out of the exhaust
trouble codes for catalytic converter failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Dealership Failure to Perform Recall Repairs
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to perform recall repairs can lead to unresolved safety issues, which can cause accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Dealership refusal to perform recall repairs

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Catalytic converter failure can cause engine performance issues, decreased fuel efficiency, and potentially lead to engine failure, which can result in accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Engine runs rough with no power
black smoke coming out of the exhaust
trouble codes for catalytic converter failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure - Horn Relay Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the horn relay can cause a fire, potentially leading to vehicle destruction, injury, or even loss of life.
symptoms: Smoke coming from under the hood

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the keyless remote system can cause inconvenience, and in some cases, may be related to more serious electrical system failures that can lead to fires.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Electrical System Failure - Computer/ Dashboard Area
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system in the computer/dashboard area can cause a fire, potentially leading to vehicle destruction, injury, or even loss of life.
symptoms: Fire starting under the passenger side dashboard
smoke coming from under the hood.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering pump can cause a sudden loss of power steering assist, making the vehicle difficult to control, especially at low speeds, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: increased effort required to steer the vehicle
noise or whining sound from the power steering pump.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering gear box can cause a sudden loss of power steering assist, making the vehicle difficult to control, especially at low speeds, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: increased effort required to steer the vehicle
noise or grinding sound from the power steering gear box.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the vehicle to stall, resulting in loss of steering and braking power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Tank Vent Pipe and Charcoal Canister Design Defect
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design defect in the fuel tank vent pipe and charcoal canister can cause fuel to leak onto the ground, creating a fire hazard, especially when the vehicle is parked on an incline.
symptoms: fuel leaking from under the vehicle
fuel dripping from the plastic shield around the gas tank.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A malfunctioning ABS can lead to diminished braking ability, increased stopping distances, and reduced vehicle control, which can result in accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal travels too far down before engaging
brake pedal moves excessively before braking begins
